r the pouch into your refillable glass jar or any sealed container. Compact and convenient.</p>\r\n          </div>\r\n        </article>\r\n\r\n        <article style=\"flex:1 1 300px;min-width:240px;background:#fff;border:1px solid #d7c9b8;border-radius:14px;overflow:hidden;\">\r\n          <img src=\"https://memotherearthbrand.com/cdn/shop/files/4B5A5404_540x.jpg?v=1767238853\"\r\n               alt=\"Brushing with toothpaste tablets\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"width:100%;height:auto;display:block;\">\r\n          <div style=\"padding:16px;\">\r\n            <h3 style=\"margin:0 0 6px;\">Same clean, less waste</h3>\r\n            <p style=\"color:#5a6b63;margin:0;\">All the freshness and foam of regular toothpaste — without the tube and without the plastic.</p>\r\n          </div>\r\n        </article>\r\n      </div>\r\n\r\n      <div style=\"margin-top:16px;display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;justify-content:center;gap:12px;\">\r\n        <a href=\"https://memotherearthbrand.com/products/zero-waste-toothpaste-tablets\"\r\n          rel=\"noopener\"\r\n          style=\"display:inline-flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;padding:14px 22px;border-radius:999px;\r\n                 background:linear-gradient(180deg,#A1AB97,#1e6e4b);color:#fff;font-weight:800;border:0;\r\n                 box-shadow:0 10px 28px rgba(22,35,28,.10);text-decoration:none;white-space:nowrap;\">\r\n          Shop Toothpaste Tablets\r\n        </a>\r\n        <a href=\"https://memotherearthbrand.com/products/zero-waste-toothpaste-tablets-3-month-refills\"\r\n          rel=\"noopener\"\r\n          style=\"display:inline-flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;padding:14px 22px;border-radius:999px;\r\n                 background:transparent;color:#1e6e4b;font-weight:800;border:2px solid #1e6e4b;\r\n                 text-decoration:none;white-space:nowrap;\">\r\n          Get 3-Month Refill\r\n        </a>\r\n      </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n  </div>\r\n\r\n  <!-- FEATURES & BENEFITS --